**Key Security Controls**:
- **DOMPurify sanitization**: Strips all dangerous HTML/JavaScript while allowing safe formatting tags
- **Strict tag whitelist**: Only permits explicitly allowed tags like `<b>`, `<i>`, `<a>` - blocks `<script>`, `<style>`, event handlers
